data.title: Secretary General Congratulates the new Speaker of Djibouti Parliament
data.meta_description: H.E. the PUIC Secretary General, Mr. Mouhamed Khouraichi NIASS, expressed his sincere felicitations to H.E. Dileita Mohamed Dileita, on the occasion of his election as Speaker of the National Assembly of the Republic of Djibouti.
data.text:
In his message, H.E. the Secretary General also expressed his readiness for cooperation in order to enhance existing relations between the PUIC and the Djiboutian Parliament.

He wished the new Djiboutian Speaker of Parliament success in his tasks.
